item.title: Hello World
item.description: Hello, World! An introduction of William Bean Hello not-so-anonymous internet user-agent. I am William Bean, a human living on Earth in the nation of the United States of America, in the state of Illinois, in the area of the Quad Cities. I do technology stuff for a living with a little company called John Deere. Most of my hobbies also involve tinkering with technology. I also like to do pinball, legos, & biking.
